---
const jsonUrl = '/examples/ezer_frontend_output_example_v1.json';
const streamUrl = '/examples/ezer_progress_events_example.ndjson';
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Ezer Frontend Output Example</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f4efe6;
        --panel: #fffdf8;
        --ink: #1c1917;
        --muted: #57534e;
        --line: #d6d3d1;
        --accent: #9a3412;
        --accent-soft: #ffedd5;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Iowan Old Style", "Palatino Linotype", serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #fff7ed 0, var(--bg) 48%, #efe7da 100%);
        color: var(--ink);
      }
      main {
        max-width: 980px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 48px 20px 80px;
      }
      h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; }
      p { line-height: 1.65; color: var(--muted); }
      .hero {
        padding: 28px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.94), rgba(255,247,237,.88));
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(28,25,23,.08);
      }
      .hero small {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: var(--panel);
      }
      .code {
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding: 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: #171412;
        color: #f5f5f4;
        overflow-x: auto;
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      a { color: var(--accent); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <small>Ezer Example</small>
        <h1>Ezer 前端返回样例</h1>
        <p>这页展示两类前端契约：最终审计结果 JSON，以及可选的进度流事件。建议只对进度做流式输出，不对最终结论正文做流式输出。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>最终结果</h2>
          <p>一次性返回完整结构化 JSON，适合渲染结论卡、分组审计卡、来源抽屉和运行轨迹。</p>
          <p><a href={jsonUrl}>打开 JSON 样例</a></p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>进度流</h2>
          <p>建议用 SSE 或 WebSocket 只推送状态变化，例如取数、补充、复核和完成。</p>
          <p><a href={streamUrl}>打开 NDJSON 样例</a></p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>产品建议</h2>
          <p>推荐接口组合：`POST /tasks`、`GET /tasks/:id`、`GET /tasks/:id/events`。最终结论保持非流式，减少中间态误导。</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <div class="code">GET {jsonUrl}\nGET {streamUrl}</div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
